title: S16 Ep69: Supernatural News/Parashare:  The Well To Hell Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare:  The Well To Hell Edition
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare The Well To Hell Edition
Dave & Tim dig deep into the Well to Hell, one big, assed hole in the Earth that emits a foul stench and seems to stretch on for eternity. The boys also report on Strange Love from Aliens Above, to Lovers reaching through the veil of death for one last message, an evil set of Dark Jinn that happen to share the names of Dave's former in-laws, weird ghostly sightings, monster encounters and more!

Plus a Brand New Theater of the Mind!

Find all the news stories here: www.darknessradio.com/news

Sign up for a the new UFO/Dating series at: www.UFOCasting.co
